('96911','33445','5','Dreamlike apartment in a residence with botanical garden and spectacular swimming pool in Santa Ponsa '),
('96912','33446','5','The residential complex with its Mediterranean luxury apartments, the tropical vegetation, the beautiful pool area with sun terraces, garden areas and unique pool house with fireplace and bar for the relaxing hours is one of the finest in the Southwest. Underground parking and various spaces for cars, elevators and security service belong to the residence, which is located in close proximity to the coast and golf courses. The superbly equipped apartment with a floor space of 113 m² plus 33 m² terrace area provides for a living and dining area with American kitchen, dining room, laundry room and 2 bedrooms with bathroom en suite each.\r\n\r\n'),
